  <trk>
    <name>BCN-L1 — Eastern Pyrenees Weekend Loop — Day 2</name>
    <desc>Deploy from BCN and ride into the Eastern Pyrenees. Hit Vic and Coll de Nargó — 932m. Loop back to BCN over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
